Subject: Deleting System Departments is not possible
Description:
We created several system departments to test this feature, but now we want to delete them.
When clicking "Delete," an error message occurs:
"Auswahl konnte nicht gelöscht werden Sf guard group 
Die ausgewählte Abteilung konnte nicht gelöscht werden. Vergewissern Sie sich, dass die Abteilung keine zugehörigen Elemente hat."

In English:
"Selection could not be deleted Sf guard group 
The selected department could not be deleted. Make sure the department has no associated items."

We have already ensured that the department has no associated items, but maybe we missed something.
Solution_Comment__c: de-linked the groups from they were attached and then they could be deleted without error
